{"id":"T157_pattern_size","category":"pattern-match","difficulty":"easy","prompt":"파일 크기 분류: <1024 → \"small\", <1048576 → \"medium\", 그 외 \"large\". (size 500)는 \"small\".","validation":{"type":"stdout_contains","expected":"small"},"reference_solution":"(defn size [b] (cond [(< b 1024) \"small\"] [(< b 1048576) \"medium\"] [true \"large\"]))\n(println (size 500))","tags":["cond"]}
